<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[ص]</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[اللموص]</span>: الكذوب،<span class="c5"> ويقال:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>الخدّاع، قال عدي <span class="c2">«٢»</span>:<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِنك ذو عهد وذو مَصْدَقٍ ... مخالفٌ هدْي الكذوب اللَّمُوص<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
